OL,3,CCritical incident declared at two
OL,4,CMidlands hospitals
OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat two hospitals run by the University
OL,8,FHospitals of the North Midlands NHS
OL,9,FTrust.
OL,11,FThe Royal Stoke University Hospital
OL,12,Fand County Hospital in Stafford have
OL,13,Fbeen under increasing pressure since
OL,14,Fthe weekend.
OL,16,FThe Trust says patients should expect
OL,17,Fmuch longer delays than usual whilst
OL,18,Femergency departments tend to the
OL,19,Fsickest patients first.
