OL,3,CCritical incident declared at two
OL,4,CMidlands hospitals
OL,6,FUHNM says it took the decision to
OL,7,Fdeclare a critical incident after
OL,8,Fexperiencing an increase in
OL,9,Fattendances at the Emergency
OL,10,FDepartment who require an admission.
OL,12,FThe Trust says it will continue to
OL,13,Fwork with NHS and local authority
OL,14,Fpartners to ensure that people who
OL,15,Fneed hospital and emergency care can
OL,16,Fget treatment quickly.
OL,18,FIt will also work with other agencies
OL,19,Fto identify any additional support
OL,20,Fthat allows them to discharge patients
OL,21,Fwho do not require acute hospital care.
